<div class="title">Up in Smoke</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Captain+Tripps&Exact=1">Captain Tripps</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Captain Tripps. "Up in Smoke: An Experience with 2C-I (exp36693)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 12, 2004. erowid.org/exp/36693</div>

<br/>



